1
00:00:35,060 --> 00:00:35,860
Jingzhi.

2
00:00:38,260 --> 00:00:39,360
These three years,

3
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:43,430
what has that old scoundrel Yu Henian

4
00:00:43,430 --> 00:00:44,930
tortured you

5
00:00:44,930 --> 00:00:45,700
into?

6
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:53,460
Commander.

7
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,930
The two corpses outside the castration room

8
00:00:55,930 --> 00:00:57,930
have been dissolved in the dry well.

9
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:02,700
Besides,

10
00:01:03,260 --> 00:01:04,160
I noticed

11
00:01:04,160 --> 00:01:06,220
spies from the Yeting Bureau nearby.

12
00:01:06,430 --> 00:01:07,430
Should we...

13
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:11,300
Spare her.

14
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:13,460
If we touch her now,

15
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:16,100
Yu Henian will immediately know she is special.

16
00:01:16,100 --> 00:01:17,600
Pass my secret order.

17
00:01:18,260 --> 00:01:20,460
Dispatch two Tian-class shadow guards

18
00:01:20,830 --> 00:01:22,030
around the clock

19
00:01:22,430 --> 00:01:23,460
to keep a close watch on

20
00:01:23,460 --> 00:01:26,160
the Yeting Bureau's water dungeon and servants' quarters.

21
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:27,100
Yes, Commander.

22
00:01:27,260 --> 00:01:27,760
But...

23
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:29,330
what if the people from the Yeting Bureau

24
00:01:29,330 --> 00:01:31,190
dare to lay hands on Lady Qu again?

25
00:01:31,330 --> 00:01:33,000
If she loses a single hair,

26
00:01:33,930 --> 00:01:35,900
I will flay you alive.

27
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:40,460
But remember, unless absolutely necessary,

28
00:01:40,759 --> 00:01:42,900
you must never expose your identities.

29
00:01:42,900 --> 00:01:44,000
Even she

30
00:01:44,660 --> 00:01:46,759
cannot know of your existence.

31
00:01:47,030 --> 00:01:47,830
Yes.

32
00:01:54,100 --> 00:01:54,900
Jingzhi,

33
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:57,360
bear with it a little longer.

34
00:01:57,830 --> 00:02:00,690
Once I kill all the evil spirits in this deep palace,

35
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:02,300
I will get you out.

36
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:09,199
Look sharp, everyone.

37
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,699
It's a thunderstorm tonight.

38
00:02:10,699 --> 00:02:13,230
All palace gates must be carefully inspected.

39
00:02:13,230 --> 00:02:14,400
If assassins get in,

40
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:16,200
how many heads do we have to lose?

41
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:28,690
Let's go check the back door of the Yeting Bureau.

42
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:46,060
Yu Henian,

43
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:48,600
did you think three years in the water dungeon

44
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:49,860
could rot me away?

45
00:02:51,430 --> 00:02:52,460
You're wrong.

46
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:55,760
These three years

47
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:57,300
have already washed my weakness

48
00:02:57,300 --> 00:02:59,460
and naivety completely clean.

49
00:02:59,460 --> 00:03:00,530
Reborn for another life,

50
00:03:00,530 --> 00:03:02,590
I will not be a pawn to be slaughtered.

51
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:08,130
I will be the one playing the chess.

52
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:45,130
Does it hurt?

53
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,430
Qu Jingzhi.

54
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:48,160
Remember this pain.

55
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:51,600
Compared to the gut-wrenching poison in my previous life,

56
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:53,030
what is this little pain?

57
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:54,800
Compared to Ying Wujiu

58
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:57,030
having his heart pierced by iron hooks and his body shattered,

59
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:58,430
what is this little pain?

60
00:04:04,900 --> 00:04:06,200
It's almost dawn.

61
00:04:06,860 --> 00:04:09,860
A good show is about to start.

62
00:04:43,700 --> 00:04:45,360
You've got some nerve.

63
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:48,760
How dare you sneak into the Eastern Depot's castration room last night.

64
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:51,130
Trying to hook up with those castrated dogs?

65
00:04:51,130 --> 00:04:52,300
Watch your mouth, Momo.

66
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:54,700
If you ruin this body that the Prime Minister took such pains to preserve,

67
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:56,330
how many heads do you have to lose?

68
00:04:56,330 --> 00:04:57,300
You little bitch.

69
00:04:57,300 --> 00:04:59,659
You'd better pray your Shougongsha stays red.

70
00:04:59,659 --> 00:05:02,800
Otherwise, the Prime Minister will personally flay you alive.

71
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,930
You old thing, if you are in a hurry to die,

72
00:05:04,930 --> 00:05:06,260
I'll fulfill your wish.

73
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:10,700
Ah!

74
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:12,560
You little bitch!

75
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:18,300
This is a treasure bestowed by the Emperor to the Lord of Nine Thousand Years.

76
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:20,500
You don't have enough heads to chop off.

77
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:23,660
Spare my life, Eunuch!

78
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:26,000
It was that little bitch who splashed me!

79
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,730
I'm innocent!
